oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Payne children
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of children of George Sanford Payne and Hattie Bell Gartland Payne sitting on the side of a car. The children are Ruby, Ella B., Alvin, Herbert, and Loretta. Mrs. Hattie Payne and Mrs. Eliza Ethany Payne are the women seated in the car.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
